 为什么慢跑、长跑（通常称为慢跑）的练习如此广泛流行？&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What factors have contributed to the surge in popularity of jogging, which involves running at a leisurely pace over extended distances?&lt;br /&gt;
 哪些因素导致了慢跑（即以悠闲的速度长距离跑步）的流行？&lt;/li&gt;
