 慢跑可以增强心脏力量，有助于减肥。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regular jogging contributes to the fortification of the heart and aids in shedding excess weight.&lt;br /&gt;
 定期慢跑有助于增强心脏功能并有助于减肥。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;tab&#34; data-id=&#34;id4&#34; data-title=&#34;Writing&#34;&gt;
