&lt;li&gt;Jogging confers strength upon the heart and facilitates weight reduction for individuals.&lt;br /&gt;
 慢跑能增强心脏力量，有助于减轻个人体重。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The practice of jogging serves to bolster cardiac endurance and promote weight loss in individuals.&lt;br /&gt;
 慢跑有助于增强心脏耐力，促进个人减肥。&lt;/li&gt;
