&lt;li&gt;When determining the appropriate distance for jogging, it&#39;s essential to exercise caution against pushing yourself too far, too rapidly.&lt;br /&gt;
 在确定合适的慢跑距离时，一定要小心，不要把自己推得太远、太快。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bear in mind not to overexert yourself in the initial stages of jogging. Gradually increasing the distance is key.&lt;br /&gt;
 请记住，在慢跑的初始阶段不要用力过度。逐渐增加距离是关键。&lt;/li&gt;
