&lt;li&gt;Take a brief jog, ensuring you stay within your comfortable limit.&lt;br /&gt;
 进行短暂的慢跑，确保您保持在舒适的范围内。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in a few short jogging sessions, making sure not to exceed your personal comfort level.&lt;br /&gt;
 进行一些短时间的慢跑，确保不要超出您个人的舒适水平。&lt;/li&gt;
