&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subsequently, engage in brief jogging intervals, being mindful not to surpass your established threshold of comfort.&lt;br /&gt;
 随后，进行短暂的慢跑，注意不要超过既定的舒适阈值。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proceed to conduct abbreviated jogging routines, taking care not to surpass the boundaries of your individualized comfort tolerance.&lt;br /&gt;
 继续进行简短的慢跑程序，注意不要超出您个人舒适度的界限。&lt;/li&gt;
